<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title>Your Invoice from
			{{ organization_name }}</title>
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				background-color: #f4f4f4;
				color: #333;
				padding: 20px;
			}
			.container {
				background-color: #fff;
				padding: 30px;
				border-radius: 8px;
				box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			}
			.header {
				font-size: 20px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				color: #2c3e50;
			}
			.invoice-details {
				margin: 20px 0;
			}
			.invoice-details table {
				width: 100%;
				border-collapse: collapse;
			}
			.invoice-details th,
			.invoice-details td {
				padding: 10px;
				text-align: left;
				border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
			}
			.total {
				font-size: 16px;
				font-weight: bold;
				margin-top: 20px;
			}
			.footer {
				margin-top: 30px;
				font-size: 12px;
				color: #888;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="header">Hello
				{{ patient_name }},</div>

			<p>Thank you for your visit. Please find the details of your invoice below:</p>

			<div class="invoice-details">
				<table>
					<tr>
						<th>Description</th>
						<th>Amount</th>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>{{ invoice.description }}</td>
						<td>${{ invoice.amount|number_format(2) }}</td>
					</tr>
				</table>

				<p class="total">Total: ${{ invoice.amount|number_format(2) }}</p>
			</div>

			<p>If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>

			<p>Regards,<br>{{ organization_name }}
				Team</p>

			<div class="footer">
				This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
